<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n38096g"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n38" href="#n38096g">N38 (VI.B.32)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n38all.htm#n38096g"> 96(g)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> hiring fairs </blockquote> <dd class="well"><mm class="note">Note: Hiring Fairs: forerunners of modern employment exchanges; they used to be held annually in English and Welsh market-towns. Men and women would stand in rows to be inspected by those seeking farm workers or servants. </mm> </dd></dl>
